0Z","msg":"<blockquote>沙比都有馬斯幫手<br />\n<br />\n佢得個藍斯 仲要衝撚左上去唔識落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雲爺爺最鍾意一啲可以比人無限中出嘅中場配搭<br />\n明知渣㗎本身慢 佢就偏偏要藍斯打B2B 留低渣㗎自己一個係中圈前自爆<br />\n渣㗎同太子兩個都係組織型 又偏偏要兩個一齊出<br />\n最過癮係搞左咁耐 全隊一隊竟然得返一個正統防中 仲要正選唔用佢 <br />\n呢啲用人哲學我真係理解唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d6e5dfb305ab936813b577882fafb0f6c95f19","tid":507090,"uid":132961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c93e5a6a97b103a0932829d01157612215d0a57","tid":507090,"uid":38172,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T04:03:59.000Z","msg":"矛盾角色因佢係 叫沙加。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"笑左 又岩音喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc96f7af62a842560aa16b3320da767894a9869","tid":507090,"uid":132961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f756a6eaa6fa2abbe89a16b1b64da57bb56c5808","tid":507090,"uid":44638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:07:37.000Z","msg":"咁易甩波點打攻中<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:44:10.000Z","msg":"打攻中安全過打防中 防中一甩就直接對啞仔細梅"},{"pid":"38e662353072a997eca08ffa176d8a2cee09d4a0","tid":507090,"uid":31841,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"長傳準，有遠射，根本係屎高斯類型中場<br />\n偏偏條弱智死老野搵佢打防中<br />\n你仲想佢有咩表現"},{"pid":"66a89f52f33fbeadc342ea32e6ebf51f7eacfc2e","tid":507090,"uid":59678,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>矛盾角色因佢係 叫沙加。。。</blockquote>笑左 又岩音喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/23/155930_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F23%2F155930_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22